title: Match of the Day 2 - S10E06 - 20th September 2015 - 720p x264

SPORT: Match of the Day 2
On: BBC 2 HD     
Date: Sunday 20th September 2015 
Time: 22:00 to 23:10 

Mark Chapman introduces highlights and analysis of the day's three Premier League matches plus a round-up of the weekend's earlier action. Southampton face Manchester United, a side they beat for the first time in 12 league and cup meetings when they last played. Norwich travel to Liverpool, looking for their first win at Anfield since 1994, whilst the day's other match is a London derby at White Hart Lane between Tottenham and Crystal Palace.
